title: Interested in a townhome loft? We've got one, call us for more info~!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Glen Park, where apartments are spacious, and grounds are just a beautiful as a picture.', 'We offer 1-3 bedroom floor plans with something that will work for everyone.', 'All homes have a full size washer and dryer as well as wood burning fireplaces.', 'We strive to find the right price and floorplan that will work for you.', 'We have a mixture of townhomes and flats.', 'Along with our lovely apartments, you can enjoy some of our generous amenities: When you move in, you can relax and lounge by our sparkling outdoor pool, and year-round you can relax in the heated spa or sauna.', 'Feeling athletic?', 'Come in and get your work out 24 hours 7 days a week in our deluxe fitness center.', 'You can bring your furry friend to the on-site dog park or get in a game of tennis on the court.', 'You can find all of our pricing and availability on our website.', 'Call us to schedule a tour our office hours are:', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 am - 6:00 pm', 'Sat: 10:00 am - 5:00 pm', 'Sun: 10:00 am - 5:00 pm', 'Photos on this ad may not reflect all floor plans and trim.', 'Advertised pricing and availability are subject to change without notice and cannot be guaranteed.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'No soliciting.']
